reviewText: She is a girly girl and this fits her perfectly.  She has great attention span, however, this little movie is active enough to keep any little one entranced.  A great gift from grandparents, aunts and great grandparents.
My 3-year old about wore out the others.  It was a nice break from what she was used to...

Strawberry Shortcake DVD's are sweet and gentle for toddler girls.  Having said that the general theme of all Strawberry Shortcake stories and episodes, including this DVD also, are rather shallow and focused on fashion and spending money on buying things for themselves.  There are some minor lessons in kindness but as I said, the overall focus self indulgence.

We collect all of the DVDs and books with these characters. They have fun stories that are full of color and fabulous fashions. Our daughter watches the DVDs over and over and never tires of the books as well.

These are great movies and my grandkids -- boy 4, girl 2 -- love watching them over and over and over and over!  The lessons they teach really seem to get across to the kids, even the 2 year old.  Just love them.
